You will need a proxy to make this work.  If you're on a mac, add a vhost to your local apache that looks like this:


<VirtualHost *:80>
   DocumentRoot /Library/WebServer/Documents/<yourfolder or symlink>
   ServerName weatherrob.local

   AcceptPathInfo On

   ProxyPass /yahooweather/ http://weather.yahooapis.com/
   ProxyPassReverse /yahooweather/ http://weather.yahooapis.com/

</VirtualHost>